title: GORG 2STORY UNIT IN MURANO South of Fifth!!!!
posting_body: ['Work / Live on the most desirable boardwalk in all of Miami.', 'Zoned commercial/residential, chose to open up your office or make this 2 story townhouse a place you call home.', 'Direct water views as well as downtown skyline views.', 'Kitchen is equipped with subzero and Miele appliances.', 'Large walk in closet.', 'Experience condo living without the hassle of elevators or having to wait on your car.', 'Parking spot is directly in front of the townhouse.', "Walk to Monty's Smith and Wollensky or Joes within minutes.", 'Murano features a world class gym, pool, tennis court, valet, security and more.', 'For those looking for commercial use, great foot traffic and plenty of parking around the area.', 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
